SUMMARY:ALL STAFF RETREAT HOLD
DESCRIPTION:"Character/Culture = Brain Science\n\nHow to use diagnostics to...\n- make individualized IXL plans for students\n- create small group intervention plans\n- comms with families\n\nSet expectations around...\n- CFA completion\n- Using CFA data to inform instruction \n- Retaking CFAs and using data for gradebooks\n- Practice CFA data analysis/looking at student work protocol for most recent CFA"	How to use Biliteracy Data (K-2 Amplify) & 3-8 Star?	Also\, get leaders the Learning Genie Assessment PD
